   West Valley Demonstration Project

   The WVDP is located on the site of the only commercial nuclear fuel
   reprocessing plant to have operated in the United States. It is
   currently generating and storing mixed waste owned by the State of New
   York and expects to generate and store mixed waste in the future. The
   site is located on 3,340 acres of state-owned land approximately 30
   miles southeast of Buffalo, New York.   West Valley Demonstration
   Project (Buffalo, NY)
